OL,3,CMan jailed after kicking out at police
OL,4,Cduring Sunderland riot
OL,6,FA man who kicked out at frontline
OL,7,Fpolice officers while wrapped in an
OL,8,FEngland flag has been jailed for four
OL,9,Fyears and eight months for his role in
OL,10,Fdisorder in Sunderland last year.
OL,12,FJohn Kirtley, of Rutherglen Road,
OL,13,FSunderland, pleaded guilty to riot and
OL,14,Fwas today (Thursday 29 February)
OL,15,Fsentenced at Newcastle Crown Court for
OL,16,Fhis role in the disorder.
OL,18,FJudge Robert Spragg, sentencing, told
OL,19,FKirtley: "You, together with many
OL,20,Fothers, brought shame upon the city of
OL,21,FSunderland.
