OL,6,F"It involved serious acts of violence
OL,7,Fagainst the persons and property.
OL,9,F"You were front and centre in most of
OL,10,Fthe footage."
OL,12,FThe 27-year-old was identified
OL,13,Ffollowing images and footage shared
OL,14,Fwith police, which included scenes of
OL,15,FKirtley kicking out at frontline
OL,16,Fofficers, and shouting "my country".
OL,18,FHe was also captured pushing a
OL,19,Fshopping trolley and kicking at police
OL,20,Fofficers.
